File and project templates for Xcode.

Clone to ~/Library/Application Support/Developer/Shared/Xcode/ or /Library/Application Support/Developer/Shared/Xcode and restart Xcode.
These templates will be added to a 'Testing' section of the New File/Project window.

The GTM example should work with OS 3.2
The GHUnit example has yet to be updated to run on 3.2/iPad

OCUnit
http://developer.apple.com/mac/articles/tools/unittestingwithxcode3.html

GTM (Google Toolbox for Mac)
http://code.google.com/p/google-toolbox-for-mac/wiki/iPhoneUnitTesting

GHUnit
http://github.com/gabriel/gh-unit

OCMock
http://www.mulle-kybernetik.com/software/OCMock/

Hamcrest
http://code.google.com/p/hamcrest/

